## SQL:
with a1 as ( select setl_id, listagg(distinct MEDINS_LIST_CODG, ',') within group (order by MEDINS_LIST_CODG) b_medins_list_codg, listagg(distinct medins_list_name, ',') within group (order by medins_list_name) b_medins_list_name, listagg(distinct f.hilist_code, ',') within group (order by f.hilist_code) b_hilist_code, listagg(distinct hilist_name, ',') within group (order by hilist_name) b_hilist_name, listagg(distinct MED_CHRGITM_TYPE_NAME, ',') within group (order by MED_CHRGITM_TYPE_NAME) MED_CHRGITM_TYPE, listagg(distinct CHRGITM_LV_NAME, ',') within group (order by CHRGITM_LV_NAME) CHRGITM_LV, listagg(distinct BILG_DEPT_NAME, ',') within group (order by BILG_DEPT_NAME) BILG_DEPT_NAME, listagg(distinct BILG_DR_NAME, ',') within group (order by BILG_DR_NAME) BILG_DR_NAME, listagg(distinct ACORD_DEPT_NAME, ',') within group (order by ACORD_DEPT_NAME) ACORD_DEPT_NAME, listagg(distinct ACORD_DR_NAME, ',') within group (order by ACORD_DR_NAME) ACORD_DR_NAME, sum(f.cnt) as b_cnt, sum(f.det_item_fee_sumamt) as b_fee, min(f.pric) as min_pric, min(abs(f.inscp_amt / f.cnt)) as min_amt from FEE_LIST_D f where f.cnt <> 0 and f.CHRGITM_LV_NAME in ('甲类','乙类') group by f.setl_id ), a2 as ( select a1.*, s.fixmedins_code, s.fixmedins_name, s.HOSP_LV_NAME, s.mdtrt_id, s.ipt_otp_no, s.psn_no, s.psn_name, s.certno, s.GEND_NAME, s.brdy, s.age, s.insu_admdvs, s.INSUTYPE_NAME, s.PSN_TYPE_NAME, s.SP_PSN_TYPE_NAME, s.med_type_name, s.PAY_LOC_NAME, s.setl_time, s.adm_dept_name, s.dscg_dept_name, s.begntime, s.endtime, s.IPT_DAYS, s.chfpdr_name, s.adm_diag_dscr, s.dscg_maindiag_name, s.DIAG_NAME, s.dise_no, s.dise_name, s.OPRN_NAME, s.medfee_sumamt, s.pool_prop_selfpay, s.hifp_pay, s.hifmi_pay, s.maf_pay, s.cvlserv_pay, s.othfund_pay, s.acct_pay, s.cash_payamt, s.fund_pay_sumamt, s.insutype, case when a1.b_cnt > (s.ipt_days *12+24) then a1.b_cnt - (s.ipt_days *12+24) else 0 end as break_cnt, case when a1.b_cnt > (s.ipt_days *12+24) then (a1.b_cnt - (s.ipt_days *12+24)) * (a1.min_pric * 1) else 0 end as break_fee, case when a1.b_cnt > (s.ipt_days *12+24) then (a1.b_cnt - (s.ipt_days *12+24)) * (a1.min_amt * 1) else 0 end as break_amt from a1 inner join SETL_D_MERGED s on a1.setl_id = s.setl_id where a1.b_cnt > (s.ipt_days *12+24) and s.FUND_PAY_SUMAMT <> 0 ) select fixmedins_code 医院代码, fixmedins_name 医院名称, HOSP_LV_NAME 医院级别, setl_id 结算单据号, mdtrt_id 就诊ID, ipt_otp_no 住院号, psn_no 个人编号, psn_name 姓名, certno 身份证号, GEND_NAME 性别, brdy 出生日期, age 年龄, insu_admdvs 统筹区, INSUTYPE_NAME 险种类型, PSN_TYPE_NAME 医疗人员类别, SP_PSN_TYPE_NAME 特殊人员身份类别, med_type_name 就医类型, PAY_LOC_NAME 支付地点类别, setl_time 结算日期, adm_dept_name 入院科室, dscg_dept_name 出院科室, begntime 入院日期, endtime 出院日期, IPT_DAYS 天数, chfpdr_name 主治医生, adm_diag_dscr 入院诊断, dscg_maindiag_name 出院诊断, DIAG_NAME 其他诊断, dise_no 病种编码, dise_name 病种名称, OPRN_NAME 手术及操作名称, medfee_sumamt 总金额, concat(to_char(pool_prop_selfpay * 100), '%') 基本医疗统筹支付比例, hifp_pay 基本医保支付, hifmi_pay 大病报销, maf_pay 医疗救助, cvlserv_pay 公务员补充, othfund_pay 其他支付, acct_pay 个人帐户支付, cash_payamt 个人现金支付, fund_pay_sumamt 基金支付总额, MED_CHRGITM_TYPE 费用类别, BILG_DEPT_NAME 开单科室名称, BILG_DR_NAME 开单医生姓名, ACORD_DEPT_NAME 受单科室名称, ACORD_DR_NAME 受单医生姓名, null 收费日期, b_medins_list_codg 违规医院项目代码, b_medins_list_name 违规医院项目名称, b_hilist_code 违规医保项目代码, b_hilist_name 违规医保项目名称, null 正常医院项目代码, null 正常医院项目名称, null 正常医保项目代码, null 正常医保项目名称, null 正常项目数量, null 正常项目金额, b_cnt 违规项目收费数量, min_pric 违规项目单价, break_cnt 违规项目数量, CHRGITM_LV 违规项目支付类别, break_fee 违规项目金额, break_amt 违规项目范围内金额, gettcamount(break_amt, pool_prop_selfpay, hifp_pay, fund_pay_sumamt) 基本统筹违规金额, getdbamount(break_amt, insutype, hifmi_pay, fund_pay_sumamt) 大病统筹违规金额, GETMAFAMOUNT(break_amt, maf_pay, fund_pay_sumamt) 医疗救助违规金额, case when substr(INSU_ADMDVS,1,4) != '{pool_no}' then '是' else '否' end 是否异地, 'CB_0020' 违规规则代码, '超标准收费' 违规类型, '按小时收费的血液净化类诊疗项目（如自动腹膜透析、连续性血液净化等），收费数量超过实际提供的诊疗服务数量。' 违规事项, '《江西省医疗服务价格项目目录（2023年修订版）》中血液净化类诊疗项目收费的真实性。' 违规依据 from a2

